---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon';
---

<section class="py-24 bg-cream">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="h-px w-12 bg-burgundy/30"></div>
              <span class="text-burgundy font-medium tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">About Me</span>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl text-burgundy mb-8">Blending Technology & Culinary Arts</h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6 text-olive-dark">
              <p>
                By day, I'm a software developer crafting digital experiences. But when I step away from the keyboard, you'll find me in the kitchen, experimenting with flavors and techniques from around the world.
              </p>
              <p>
                Growing up in an Italian family, food was always at the heart of our gatherings. Those early experiences sparked a lifelong passion for cooking that has grown alongside my tech career. While I may not be a professionally trained chef, my approach to cooking mirrors my approach to coding: it's all about understanding the fundamentals, being precise with techniques, and not being afraid to experiment.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-olive">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-burgundy/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <Icon name="heroicons-outline:code" class="w-5 h-5 text-burgundy" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-medium">Tech Background</div>
                  <div class="text-sm">Full Stack Developer</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-olive">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-burgundy/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <Icon name="heroicons-outline:heart" class="w-5 h-5 text-burgundy" />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="font-medium">Culinary Focus</div>
                  <div class="text-sm">Italian & French Cuisine</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Image -->
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-4 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
              <img 
                src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3814446/pexels-photo-3814446.jpeg" 
                alt="Luigi in the kitchen" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 